reviewText: Big fan of the series. Is so good to be able to stop, back up and replay a scene or interaction between the players to get a little something extra out of it or pick up on something you might have missed in the original showing on the air. Title: Ncis Ten Season Pack

reviewText: I had the seasons recorded on my DVR, but they were out of order and I was missing a lot of them. Now I can watch them in order and enjoy them back-to-back. The only problem with watching them endlessly is that I'v discovered that, although I think Abbey is a great character, her childlike persona whenever Gibbs is around is pretty darn annoying.  I REALLY hate that Ziva left. My son got me hooked on it and I usually don't watch TV.
summary: Can't get enough of this show
Title: Ncis Ten Season Pack

reviewText: I would recommend this bundle for fans of NCIS as it would much more expensive to buy all of the DVDs indiivially. It makes a great gift for fans of the series.
summary: Great Value for Fans of The Series
Title: Ncis Ten Season Pack

reviewText: I really enjoy NCIS and I love to have the original shows to watch again,  Delivery was prompt.  There were warnings on the packages about close captions being on some of the disks,  Season 2 had closed captions on some of the disks which would not turn off when I tried to clear them with my machines viewing options. They appear to have been recorded with the closed captions on and it made them unable to be cleared,  That was a little annoying but all the other seasons played well.  The disk information did warn me so I guess I shouldn't complain..
summary: Good history for my current favorate show

reviewText: We watched this series back when it first appeared and enjoyed it very much. We consider this to be an example of what might be called, the perfect television series. One which is decent, entertaining, interesting, and fast moving. Over the years, we missed quite a few of them for various reasons, and now have a chance to catch up. It will take a long time to go through all of the stories, but we're looking forward to every moment of it.
summary: Bringing the good old times up to date.

reviewText: There are reasons why this is such a powerful TV series, why it has lasted so long.  They may vary from person to person, but I will try to share my view.  The cast interacts like a good family, in kind of an "Ozzie and Harriet" way.  Everything is condensed and developing character and plot so as to not become dull or boring.  The stories can seem a little outlandish, but the cast brings everything together quite well.  As a military retiree I salute the CID and NCIS and all the military agencies that are out there doing a hard job that is not so glamorous as can be portrayed on a one hour TV slot.
Title: Ncis Ten Season Pack

reviewText: This is one of the best law enforcement based shows ever.  It has a great cast of characters.  S/A Leroy Jethro Gibbs and Ziva David are my favorite characters followed by the flamboyant Abby Shuto and Ducky - the medical examiner.  The late Mike Franks was a good character, as well as, Jenny - Shepard, the former Director of NCIS.Leon Vance has grown on me over time along with S/A Magee and S/A Di Nozzo.
Title: Ncis Ten Season Pack
